Definition: exhibiting lack of respect
Example: rude and discourteous; remarks disrespectful of the law; disrespectful in the presence of his parents; disrespectful toward his teacher
Synonyms: RESPECTFUL, IMMODEST, DISCOURTEOUS, IRREVERENT, OFFENSIVE, SARCASTIC, exhibiting, lack, of, respect, rude, and, discourteous, remarks, disrespectful, the, law, in, presence, his, parents, toward, teacher
Category: adj.all
